                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381126-46-offence-1 t18381126-cd-44"></join>3rd of Octo<lb></lb>ber</rs>, I pewter pot, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; I quarter of a pint of gin, value 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 2 half-crowns, and 15 shillings; the goods and monies of <persName id="t18381126-name-352" type="victimName">
