               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. Mr. Griggs was out when I went to the bar for the</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183811260057"></xptr>
               <p>gin, and the daughter gave it me—I brought the pint pot back, and left nearly half my clothes behind—I was intoxicated when I went away.</p>
